Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Infinite Tic-Tac-Toe game with AI opponents
 InfiniTTT is a tic-tac-toe game with an infinite board and multiple
 AI opponents. The game includes both a command-line interface and a
 graphical Qt-based interface.
 .
 Features:
  - Infinite expandable game board
  - Multiple AI difficulty levels (Smart Random, Hybrid Evaluator)
  - Zoomable and pannable GUI board view
  - Touch gesture support for mobile devices
  - Win by getting 5 in a row